24. Treatment with systemic immunosuppressive medication within 2 weeks prior to initiation of study treatment, or anticipation of need for systemic immunosuppressive medication during study treatment;
25. History of severe allergic anaphylactic reactions to chimeric or humanized antibodies or fusion proteins;
